  "text": "Section 4 concerns the derivation of numerous local approximations of various degrees of accuracy for the same class of the BPS's as those dealt with in [CITATION_1] . Also, we correct and refine [CITATION_2] Theorem 3] , where the second-order local approximation for these BPS's was constructed (see Corollary 4.1). The proof of this result involves the derivation of a refinement of the local Poisson-exponential approximation for the Pólya-Aeppli family, which is given as Theorem 3.10 of Section 3. The necessary background on the Poissonexponential class is provided in Section 3.",
